She has had a traumatic time since photos emerged of her husband with his hand around her neck.

But Nigella Lawson would appear to have turned a corner after filing for divorce from millionaire art dealer Charles Saatchi, 70, last month.

With her head held high and the trace of a smile on her lips, the television cook, 53, looked happy and confident as she left a central London hairdresser’s on Saturday. Even the rain, which caused her to put her newly-done hair up in a chignon, couldn’t change her mood.

